149
00:15:27.958 --> 00:15:29.250
Brother ma was killed?

150
00:15:29.917 --> 00:15:31.042
What happened?

151
00:15:31.250 --> 00:15:32.625
Someone testified.

152
00:15:32.708 --> 00:15:33.667
