186
00:17:17.417 --> 00:17:20.625
Please think twice!

187
00:17:34.833 --> 00:17:36.042
Just by this letter?

188
00:17:36.083 --> 00:17:38.375
Your murder of vice master ma

189
00:17:38.958 --> 00:17:41.000
