190
00:17:41.125 --> 00:17:42.125
But...

191
00:17:42.792 --> 00:17:44.958
You are a khitan!

192
00:17:45.333 --> 00:17:47.167
Not only do we have physical evidence.

193
00:17:47.292 --> 00:17:49.167
