250
00:20:23.875 --> 00:20:24.875
I'll go first!

251
00:20:28.292 --> 00:20:29.458
What do you want?

252
00:20:29.542 --> 00:20:30.792
You four elders

253
00:20:33.000 --> 00:20:34.583
